                            <comment id="13279682" author="mathos" created="Sun, 20 May 2012 07:03:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I can confirm this issue still exists in 3.6.  And the patch appears to be sufficient for this fix.  Is it possible top get this pushed?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
