                            <comment id="13594260" author="hossman" created="Wed, 6 Mar 2013 02:39:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;From what i can tell, this bug was fixed in Solr 4.0 as a result of other changes/fixes to replication.&lt;/p&gt;

