Committed revision 1453149.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Can folks who have mentioned encountering this problem please verify whether they are reproducing this problem with 4.x or just 3.x versions of Solr?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;if you are reproducing it with a 4.x version, please provide specifics about which version, and any details you can about what you are doing prior to querying the details command (logs from the slave in question would help)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If all of the known instances of this bug are in fact from 3.x, i&apos;m inclined to mark it resolved as of 4.0.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
